parameters: Hello, and welcome to VS Twitch mode!
Your object here is easy: survive.
Every 20 to 30 seconds, chat will be given the option
to vote for an event. If no one votes, a random event
in Move or Die, as the name suggests, your objective
is to stay on the move and avoid the fire balls
Theres a labyrinth, where you got to escape within
Questions will ask chat a random question that can be
answered with !yes or !no and your objective is to
Boss battle, where you'll be put in an arena and have
to survive a boss until the timer reaches 0.
Kong, on which a big enemy will throw rocks at you,
and your objective is to go up and reach said enemy.
Surviving each will earn you money that can be spent
buying food and upgrading your weapon
Every 60 seconds, chat can use !invade to spawn an
enemy. You can defend yourself using your weapon
Finally, you need to remember to keep yourself fed
and hydrated. Press E near an apple/vegetable to eat
it or near the water bucket to drink water.
